Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make the announcements, so if you want to sit down while I make the announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so nice to see all of you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know for Arizona it's been cold weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For the rest of the country it's been nice, but anyway, there's a few little things that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one, please turn off your cell phones, and there's no filming or recording of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,event.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Line up for questions over here to my left, your right, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyone can ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We've asked that from our students that they would allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones to have an opportunity to ask, but this year we're going to have anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,can ask a question that wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The bookstore will close after the last break, so if you want anything at the bookstore,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if you'll get it at the break or now, it's about the only opportunity that you can, the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,bookstore will be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be producing these Q&As.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Q&As that we're doing this year, they're going to be produced in DVDs as well as CDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're asking everyone to sign a release form when they're in line, because the images
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,will be shown now on DVDs, so they'll be available in DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, we have Dr. Moon is here from Korea again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand up, would you please, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And she presented us with these lovely flowers, and now I'd like to introduce Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory and excelsis to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord, for this magnificent day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a Pepsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, God don't want a Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She would like you to give her a silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She already got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And she would like to have the grace of being, I don't know what that is, silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In the grace of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the grace of the teacher is what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you don't deserve it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I looked up her Good Karma account.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is involved in a silence transmission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it comes on down through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's transmitted back out to the world through the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha, when he passed the flower to Ananda,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it symbolized the passing on of that energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's silent and visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also, surprisingly, carries through the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It also carries through the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we do interviews on the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it said, yes, it transmits through the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Which I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's nice to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It transmits through the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it transmits through the voice as well as the presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because how many places can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But your voice, recorded voice, can be many places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though your physical body can only be in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So is that why when you're listening to music, such as Andrea Bocelli,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you go to that really high space when he's singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is that part of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're listening to it when he's in his voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know if he has it in his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all I can ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Bocelli have that energy in his voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Beauty and really grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he's asking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,could you please meditate with us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for one minute
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,could you do a meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for everybody for a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,well I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,if I want to do that or not
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole minute
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,oh my god
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,well we will
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,do that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a pair of lost keys in the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,bookstore if you could
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,if you've lost your keys please check there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we are all meditating
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for one minute
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be an extra charge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if it runs over
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,do an own
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,no an own is something different
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,no he didn't ask for an own
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,he asked for a meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how long is a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he asked for an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,how long it will take
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,if I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he's talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he's talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if it runs out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,check it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to check
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for what's in there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so you just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,check what's in there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,let me know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Zip it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,zip it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,zip it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and there it is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if this is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,like
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the longest minute on record.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also want to thank you for showing up in my dreams periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an extra charge for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay them at the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,About two months ago, I had an intense spiritual state arise,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and it lasted for about a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And afterwards, I felt quite devastated and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Devastated?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you call it a spiritual state?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a state was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I had sat down to contemplate because I had a lot of mental chaos going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the minute I sat down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it instantly became an awareness of the duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I heard a voice or a thought came that said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,forget about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the small self fell back,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything just, uh, lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the self as that.
