Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of existence and your own existence is divinity, and that's what you affirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just curious if it would be of any use to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
