Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see that world to see what he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And my husband dragged me here the first time a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not hearing her very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sit back just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband dragged me here about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Her husband what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragged her here about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragged her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very glad he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to ask for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of the teacher is itself the blessing and the good karma to bring that experience within your own life, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,May I touch your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from Croatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Croatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was south of Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
