Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you and ask for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a longer thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been to Croatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Croatia is very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been to Cottonwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Cottonwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that in your career, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my question is in regards to the energy in your CDs and your DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand there's energy in them, and I listen to your CDs all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have them playing, and I'm not listening to it, but it's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I still getting the energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer, we can ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so he has to have it on, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be in my ear and hearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In the similar vein, I have the DVDs playing, the volume is off, and I'm reading a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So am I getting the energy then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bizarre question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bizarre person, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me what you're getting, actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to have the radio on the car while they're driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand without actually listening to it, because that would be a distraction from
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually have no questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to just come here and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fairly new student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a very good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the first student here, so I'm very happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a very good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very good at talking, so I'm very, very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fairly new student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My son stumbled on Power vs. Force and talked about it for three months while he was digesting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, I pooh-poohed it, thinking where it was coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And after he finished the book, he gave me his copy, and it was obviously a life-changing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,experience for me, and I just wanted to take this opportunity to thank you and tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,how impressed I am with the devotional nature of your followers and the people that follow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you for coming here and affirming it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have a good son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been studying your work for about three months, but I'm very excited to see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question is, my son and his wife have been heroin addicts for three years, and they're
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,clean right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got to sit closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit just a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A little closer to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My son and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son and your daughter-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't get along very well, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you that, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the typical mother-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to be good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hard to be good, isn't it?
