Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be consistent, then, you be as loving as you can be as a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If lovingness is your way of being in the world, then it's not affected by what's going on out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, your purpose here is to be loving as a way of being in the world.
