Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't handle it. You turn it over to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You surrender the fear to God. You surrender your life to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you do that, terror comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you surrender your terror to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Just surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, that's the, what carries you through all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to surrender everything to God, including your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you feel like you're dying, you say, all right, so I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And you surrender your life to God.
