Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.98,0:25:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.10,0:25:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for your body of work on disease and recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.77,0:25:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's huge.
