Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.50,0:25:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.22,0:25:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And how would you treat these types of diseases at your clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.98,0:25:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.77,0:25:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there mental illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.98,0:25:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants you to comment on dementia.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.14,0:25:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dementia.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.00,0:25:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.90,0:25:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And how would you look at it and how would you treat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.14,0:26:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I would look at it as premature aging and the mind is aged.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.53,0:26:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, usually chronic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.22,0:26:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It occurs, you know, old age, and it's just a natural wearing out of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.98,0:26:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way I look at it, the natural wearing out of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.98,0:26:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain fag.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.98,0:26:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I used to tell patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.98,0:26:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, what's wrong with me, doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.98,0:26:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.98,0:26:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, well, it's just brain fag.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.98,0:26:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody was happy with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.98,0:26:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a little case of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.98,0:26:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain fag.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.98,0:26:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.98,0:26:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.98,0:26:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.98,0:26:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.98,0:26:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.98,0:26:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.98,0:26:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.98,0:26:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.98,0:26:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.98,0:26:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.98,0:26:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.98,0:26:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.98,0:26:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.98,0:26:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.98,0:26:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.98,0:26:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.98,0:26:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain fag sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.98,0:26:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Accepted as normal evolution in the human domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.98,0:26:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the story you told about when you went to the rest homes and the little
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.38,0:26:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,old lady, you know, would be sitting there and they say, what did you have for dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.92,0:26:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.92,0:26:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.92,0:26:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that story that you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.92,0:27:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That she'd already crossed over, you know, to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.92,0:27:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not close enough to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.74,0:27:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.74,0:27:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, do you remember the story about the little old lady that you would go see when
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.74,0:27:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you would visit the rest homes and you would ask her, well, what'd you eat today?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And she couldn't answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.74,0:27:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.74,0:27:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said she was perfectly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.18,0:27:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the people around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.38,0:27:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.38,0:27:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the people around her that are disturbed by dementia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.12,0:27:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who has dementia has already forgotten that he's forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.74,0:27:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.74,0:27:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say, how are you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.74,0:27:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.74,0:27:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what day it is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.74,0:27:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.74,0:27:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.74,0:27:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.74,0:27:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It worries the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.74,0:27:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, grandpa doesn't remember what, what day it is anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.74,0:27:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should he remember what day it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.74,0:27:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who needs to know what day it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.74,0:28:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what day it is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.74,0:28:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't really worry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.74,0:28:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what day it is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.74,0:28:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.74,0:28:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as somebody knows what day it is, yeah, you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.74,0:28:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They might pawn off yesterday's newspaper on you and you didn't know it, you know what
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.74,0:28:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.74,0:28:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.74,0:28:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way I tell what day it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.74,0:28:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I go and I look at the newspaper and it says right up there, the Arizona Republic, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.74,0:28:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.74,0:28:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't find out what day it is on Fox News, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.74,0:28:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't tell you what day it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.74,0:28:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.74,0:28:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.74,0:28:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.74,0:28:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.74,0:28:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.74,0:28:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.74,0:28:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sit back, just a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.74,0:28:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.74,0:28:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.74,0:28:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.74,0:28:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, hi, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.74,0:28:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.74,0:28:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.74,0:28:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.74,0:28:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.74,0:28:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.74,0:28:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.74,0:28:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.74,0:28:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.74,0:28:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.74,0:28:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.74,0:29:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.74,0:29:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.74,0:29:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.74,0:29:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.74,0:29:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.74,0:29:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.74,0:29:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.74,0:29:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.74,0:29:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Souto's amigo, Hachikamana.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.74,0:29:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.74,0:29:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I just want to thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.33,0:29:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, Buddhas said transcend your six sense into wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.74,0:29:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wondered if you can give me a practical examples about how you can transcend the taste,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.74,0:29:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,sense of taste, into wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.74,0:29:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Which you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.74,0:29:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How to transcend, just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.74,0:29:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,taste. Sixth sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.18,0:29:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Into wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.51,0:29:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Into wisdom. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.24,0:29:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sixth sense is? Like just give an
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.50,0:29:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,example of like you said
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.66,0:29:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,one sense which is taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.38,0:29:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way you can transcend
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.22,0:29:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,like eating a chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.20,0:29:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.77,0:29:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.48,0:30:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,very well. I know Dave. I'm trying to think
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.57,0:30:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,how to put it to you so you don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.74,0:30:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What she wants to know
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.83,0:30:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.46,0:30:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,said to transcend
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.09,0:30:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,your sixth sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.50,0:30:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.51,0:30:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And that into wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.44,0:30:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So what she's
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.27,0:30:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,asking you is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.59,0:30:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,such as taste
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.40,0:30:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,how would you. Such as what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.46,0:30:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste. Taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.51,0:30:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The senses. The physical senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.90,0:30:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste. Yeah. How would you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.07,0:30:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,transform that into wisdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.74,0:30:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You can't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.51,0:30:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.51,0:30:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.50,0:30:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.83,0:30:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why not many people are enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.83,0:30:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of a bum direction isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.55,0:30:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.94,0:30:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform your taste into
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.50,0:30:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.74,0:30:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean that's nonsensical.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.85,0:31:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well the sixth sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.75,0:31:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The senses. Yes. All the senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.96,0:31:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All the senses. And he says take those
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.55,0:31:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,senses and change it into
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.37,0:31:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,wisdom. The sixth sense. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.17,0:31:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Change it into wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.46,0:31:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep surrendering your will
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.53,0:31:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to God all the time and forget all
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.37,0:31:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,those cookbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.89,0:31:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer your senses into wisdom. I mean that sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.39,0:31:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.55,0:31:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Buddha's not around
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.31,0:31:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.75,0:31:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.89,0:31:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.53,0:31:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You come back talk. Talk. Sense
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.51,0:31:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.96,0:31:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter. So what
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.39,0:31:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,does he really mean when he said
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.39,0:31:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that? Yeah. When he said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.42,0:31:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your interpretation of it when he
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.46,0:31:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,said that? To surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.63,0:31:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,all
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.31,0:31:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as it occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.50,0:31:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.96,0:31:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in a
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.24,0:31:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,permanent state of surrenderingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.68,0:32:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.03,0:32:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a continuous
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.16,0:32:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,process with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.82,0:32:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.66,0:32:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.22,0:32:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you allow that state
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.00,0:32:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.54,0:32:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say flow of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.96,0:32:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You allow the state to flow of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.88,0:32:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.12,0:32:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,say next. You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.82,0:32:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.96,0:32:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,demand that you tell me what you're
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.08,0:32:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,going to say next.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.40,0:32:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say next is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.82,0:32:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you say next. And I have no
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.86,0:32:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,position about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.28,0:32:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.94,0:32:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,non-positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.72,0:32:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.16,0:32:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I remember you said
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.18,0:32:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that just be the best of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.96,0:32:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.72,0:32:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty much it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.08,0:32:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She remembers you saying
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.20,0:32:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,be the best of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.96,0:32:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.70,0:33:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,try and do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.84,0:33:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.24,0:33:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.44,0:33:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.56,0:33:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be the best doggy you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.10,0:33:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.12,0:33:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your paw.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.30,0:33:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.94,0:33:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I give God my paw.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.04,0:33:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's up to God
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.14,0:33:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what he does with my paw.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.34,0:33:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.76,0:33:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.06,0:33:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.54,0:33:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a happy dog. Be a happy doggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.58,0:33:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,People say how do you reach enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.76,0:33:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oink.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.86,0:33:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be a happy dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.76,0:33:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep wagging your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.24,0:33:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining and carrying on
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.28,0:33:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and fussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.66,0:33:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just try to keep my tail wagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.64,0:33:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.56,0:33:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.04,0:33:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog wags her tail at me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.90,0:33:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in the morning and I wag my tail back
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.56,0:33:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're all happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.72,0:33:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.92,0:33:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.34,0:34:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Love all of life unconditionally
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.62,0:34:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.86,0:34:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the doggy's tail wags.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.24,0:34:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.55,0:34:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.86,0:34:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you love everything
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.42,0:34:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,continuously no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.44,0:34:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.05,0:34:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.36,0:34:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.86,0:34:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.98,0:34:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.80,0:34:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What daily prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.32,0:34:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and practices would be useful
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.24,0:34:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for a spiritual student
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.84,0:34:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,seeking enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.86,0:34:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What daily practices
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.62,0:34:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,would be suitable
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.59,0:34:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for a student in daily practices?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.24,0:34:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's written extensively
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.57,0:34:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world of literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.82,0:34:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really asking me the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.90,0:34:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever hear meditation?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.64,0:34:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.90,0:34:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.32,0:34:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.44,0:34:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.57,0:34:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your question again?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.72,0:35:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What daily prayers and practices
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.62,0:35:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,would be useful for a spiritual student?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.59,0:35:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Daily?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.90,0:35:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What daily prayers and practices?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.03,0:35:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.96,0:35:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So meditation is the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.03,0:35:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And prayers are
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.14,0:35:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,prayers of thanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.12,0:35:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.16,0:35:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,divine requests of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.59,0:35:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, please help me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.84,0:35:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,put my socks on the right feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.46,0:35:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.48,0:35:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.30,0:35:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.51,0:35:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.55,0:35:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.82,0:35:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.09,0:35:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.18,0:35:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.42,0:35:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.46,0:35:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.50,0:35:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.59,0:35:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.67,0:35:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The big payoff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.25,0:35:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic prayer that,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.57,0:35:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, instantly you're enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.55,0:35:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.46,0:35:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.17,0:35:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care about being enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.40,0:35:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The only people who care about being enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.17,0:35:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,are people who are not enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.36,0:35:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.13,0:35:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.07,0:35:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The world would call it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.77,0:35:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it calls it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.71,0:35:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.50,0:35:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll put you in a, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.48,0:35:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,funny house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.81,0:35:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.53,0:36:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.77,0:36:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.40,0:36:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.00,0:36:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.19,0:36:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.23,0:36:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.29,0:36:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.33,0:36:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.38,0:36:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.40,0:36:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.46,0:36:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.48,0:36:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They put you in the funny farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.07,0:36:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.90,0:36:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.38,0:36:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, let's picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.36,0:36:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.69,0:36:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.46,0:36:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you've made in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.51,0:36:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as my brother's
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.61,0:36:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.01,0:36:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.17,0:36:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.96,0:36:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.05,0:36:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.78,0:36:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.05,0:36:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.55,0:36:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.84,0:36:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.63,0:36:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.07,0:36:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is somebody enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.19,0:36:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or are they retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.19,0:36:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.19,0:36:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.05,0:36:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.19,0:36:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.38,0:37:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.38,0:37:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.05,0:37:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.07,0:37:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.13,0:37:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.15,0:37:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.51,0:37:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.53,0:37:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.75,0:37:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.82,0:37:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.03,0:37:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're politically correct today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.69,0:37:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.75,0:37:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.67,0:37:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.34,0:37:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.13,0:37:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.00,0:37:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.13,0:37:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,from the book I.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.05,0:37:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.57,0:37:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to read
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.61,0:37:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,two sentences
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.65,0:37:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then ask
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.50,0:37:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.67,0:37:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One can view
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.71,0:37:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual ego
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.96,0:37:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as the current manifestation of one's karma
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.36,0:37:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so that undoing the ego is the same
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.67,0:37:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as resolving one's karma
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.88,0:37:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because they are operationally one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.90,0:37:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If the term karma is not acceptable,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,one can use the term unconscious instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.07,0:37:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.86,0:37:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how is undoing the ego and karma operationally the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.05,0:38:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.38,0:38:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is a karmic creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.70,0:38:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one's inner attitude towards that ego
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.70,0:38:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is one's spiritual state.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.86,0:38:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to take it seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.88,0:38:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to throw yourself down a well
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.66,0:38:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because your ego is condemning you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.82,0:38:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the inner attitude is one of humility
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.76,0:38:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrender without identifying with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.51,0:38:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The human condition is, you see, what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.59,0:38:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the human brain operates
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.28,0:38:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's our karmic inheritance as human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.22,0:38:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I always respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.86,0:38:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if God's will is for me to have a brain that functions that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.01,0:39:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,who am I to tell God that he's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.20,0:39:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.78,0:39:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you accept with humility the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.28,0:39:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.18,0:39:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to personalize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.62,0:39:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just accept it's the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.12,0:39:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.86,0:39:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have two arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.90,0:39:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you don't have five?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.34,0:39:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you don't have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.30,0:39:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.20,0:39:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's dumb to keep asking questions
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.28,0:39:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,about why is everything the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.55,0:39:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that it's God's will that it be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.20,0:39:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.30,0:39:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just surrender it to the creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.22,0:39:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.16,0:39:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God was bored, so he created human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.48,0:39:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's regretted it ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.22,0:40:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Never got a good night's rest anymore since I created humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.22,0:40:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always some prayer bouncing off the floor of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.22,0:40:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.22,0:40:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.22,0:40:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.22,0:40:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.22,0:40:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.22,0:40:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.22,0:40:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to, I'm just here to thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.22,0:40:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.22,0:40:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.22,0:40:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.22,0:40:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.22,0:40:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.22,0:40:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.22,0:40:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.22,0:40:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.22,0:40:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.22,0:40:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, for taking a machete to my ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.22,0:40:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.84,0:40:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.22,0:40:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.22,0:40:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we drowned it, too, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.22,0:40:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.22,0:40:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we drowned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.22,0:40:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we used a machete.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.02,0:40:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Other times, we just drowned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.22,0:40:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.22,0:40:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drown it in pea soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.96,0:40:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.22,0:40:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.22,0:40:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.22,0:40:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.08,0:40:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.22,0:40:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to come
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.42,0:40:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,actually offering, bringing something to you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.34,0:40:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to both of you to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.56,0:40:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was praying and asked God to show me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.12,0:41:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing came
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.04,0:41:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just wanted to offer my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.98,0:41:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and just
