Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.30,0:46:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.66,0:46:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.98,0:46:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and receive a blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.50,0:46:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.46,0:46:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.28,0:46:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.16,0:46:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.57,0:46:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.16,0:46:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.74,0:46:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ah
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.61,0:46:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,now he brings in the picture
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.42,0:46:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.34,0:46:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,ouch
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.42,0:46:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.22,0:46:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,his thumb's in there
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.38,0:46:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.90,0:46:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.90,0:46:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.90,0:46:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,smile
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.92,0:46:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there you go
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.98,0:46:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.82,0:46:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.82,0:46:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ouch
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.32,0:46:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ouch
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.28,0:46:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,ouch
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.38,0:46:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.74,0:46:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.09,0:46:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hello doc
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.07,0:47:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said in the audience in the audience lots of times
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.61,0:47:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and ah
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.22,0:47:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like for probably like a few weeks after
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.46,0:47:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a real subtle energy
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.61,0:47:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.38,0:47:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be very subtle
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.90,0:47:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think that the fact is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.53,0:47:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that I feel alive
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.90,0:47:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I can this
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.66,0:47:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,one day
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.57,0:47:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.01,0:47:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.40,0:47:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That feels really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.92,0:47:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But last time I actually came up on stage
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.03,0:47:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and for about a month after that I could barely function.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.98,0:47:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.50,0:47:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could feel an energy from my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.28,0:47:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,right up through my spine at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.59,0:47:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it felt wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.53,0:47:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering how much proximity has to do
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.86,0:47:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with maybe the transmission we get from the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.88,0:47:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He came up on stage and asked a question last time
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.78,0:47:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and he wants to know how much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.84,0:47:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, physical proximity is necessary, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.09,0:48:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise I could retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.53,0:48:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.90,0:48:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.84,0:48:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.26,0:48:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.03,0:48:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, unfortunately, physical proximity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.66,0:48:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it does go through the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.38,0:48:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy does go through the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.38,0:48:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the energy does go through the voice
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.86,0:48:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without the physical proximity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.57,0:48:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was pleased to learn that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.88,0:48:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.86,0:48:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In contemplation, it's like I'm in a field of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.59,0:48:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And wherever attention goes, the love is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.16,0:48:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I close my eyes in meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.32,0:49:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the love rapidly falls away until it's unnoticeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.38,0:49:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When he closes his eyes in meditation, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.53,0:49:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The love falls away and it's unnoticeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.09,0:49:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.86,0:49:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It shifts and the love no longer is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.07,0:49:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the love is not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.46,0:49:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.64,0:49:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know if that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.12,0:49:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it is a problem, I'd like to know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.42,0:49:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if there's a different approach to meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.59,0:49:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that would prevent the love falling away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.88,0:49:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of the presence of love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.62,0:49:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on whether you have your eyes open or closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.28,0:49:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.14,0:49:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.26,0:49:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.12,0:49:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.64,0:49:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually it is that you feel the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.42,0:49:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when you close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.84,0:49:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it disappears when you open them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.60,0:49:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the way it is with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.60,0:49:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.48,0:49:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.22,0:49:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.40,0:49:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.10,0:49:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.32,0:49:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.66,0:49:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you got your clothes on backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.55,0:50:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.44,0:50:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, if it was the reverse,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.40,0:50:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,what would be your suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.57,0:50:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's experiencing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.84,0:50:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's experiencing the world as divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.64,0:50:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.01,0:50:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when he shuts his eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.60,0:50:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he shuts out the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.92,0:50:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but he doesn't keep including himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.32,0:50:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If he included himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.01,0:50:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,which is also divine,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.26,0:50:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then it wouldn't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.05,0:50:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.74,0:50:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saying God is only out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.51,0:50:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but not just in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.07,0:50:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.55,0:50:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't exclude God
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.44,0:50:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as the source of your consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.84,0:50:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't exclude God
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.92,0:50:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as the source of your consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.57,0:50:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what is telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.72,0:50:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all these things that you're reporting
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.20,0:50:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,except the presence of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.80,0:50:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as your consciousness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.80,0:50:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can hardly refute it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.48,0:50:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when that's the very thing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.76,0:50:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're reporting, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.03,0:51:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.92,0:51:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.70,0:51:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.00,0:51:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.42,0:51:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.10,0:51:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.94,0:51:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.84,0:51:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.46,0:51:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.78,0:51:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.36,0:51:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had several spiritual experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.66,0:51:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can verbalize,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.60,0:51:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I had one that I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.76,0:51:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.03,0:51:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could calibrate that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.98,0:51:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and also if you would
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.78,0:51:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.96,0:51:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.00,0:51:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.03,0:51:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.07,0:51:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.12,0:51:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.14,0:51:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.16,0:51:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.18,0:51:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.20,0:51:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.22,0:51:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.24,0:51:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.30,0:51:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.53,0:51:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.55,0:51:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.57,0:51:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.60,0:51:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.62,0:51:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.66,0:51:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.68,0:51:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.84,0:51:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.22,0:51:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's had a couple
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.05,0:51:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.51,0:51:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.34,0:51:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've had one
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.68,0:51:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can't verbalize at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.90,0:51:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've had others
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.36,0:51:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.90,0:51:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.10,0:51:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.70,0:51:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's had one experience
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.00,0:51:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that she can't verbalize.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.50,0:51:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.00,0:52:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't verbalize it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.88,0:52:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And the others, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.14,0:52:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,she could,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.62,0:52:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is one experience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.50,0:52:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,she had that she can't verbalize.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.92,0:52:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.53,0:52:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The more the advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.88,0:52:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.84,0:52:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the more the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.96,0:52:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.68,0:52:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the less it's capable
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.32,0:52:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of being verbalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.94,0:52:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.96,0:52:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.74,0:52:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.02,0:52:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and it cannot be described
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.74,0:52:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.76,0:52:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.56,0:52:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.52,0:52:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.30,0:52:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than the appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.70,0:52:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's no way
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.50,0:52:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to explain that to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.08,0:52:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like seeing beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.82,0:52:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.38,0:52:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.65,0:52:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.73,0:52:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,out there in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.35,0:52:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.42,0:52:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.71,0:52:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.21,0:52:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.25,0:52:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.33,0:52:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.39,0:52:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's everywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.42,0:53:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.65,0:53:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.09,0:53:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So where is that beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.81,0:53:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.67,0:53:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.00,0:53:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.63,0:53:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it in the mind of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.81,0:53:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can puzzle that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.11,0:53:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,for a couple decades
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.48,0:53:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and report back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.50,0:53:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have permission
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.67,0:53:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate that experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.31,0:53:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate what experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.55,0:53:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get what experience
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.44,0:53:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.67,0:53:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hold it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.96,0:53:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't calibrate something
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.17,0:53:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't even know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.75,0:53:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hold it in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.87,0:53:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.67,0:53:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.00,0:53:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.29,0:53:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.63,0:53:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What she's holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.01,0:53:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to ask permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.33,0:53:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.85,0:53:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.98,0:53:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what she's holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.03,0:53:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.77,0:53:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.63,0:53:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because we can't identify
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.23,0:53:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.29,0:53:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.31,0:53:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's too confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.98,0:54:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.55,0:54:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.53,0:54:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.31,0:54:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.29,0:54:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody asked us
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.13,0:54:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,something simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.81,0:54:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when I walk down
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.67,0:54:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the sidewalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.40,0:54:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see little green men
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.50,0:54:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,running down.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.21,0:54:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.07,0:54:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,something simple like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.78,0:54:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here see
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.46,0:54:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the little green men
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.19,0:54:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,running around?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.32,0:54:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, volunteers,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.61,0:54:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the little green men people.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.05,0:54:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew they'd be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.03,0:54:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you can't see them
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.57,0:54:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is because they're invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.48,0:54:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.17,0:54:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.26,0:54:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,come up on stage
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.24,0:54:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and look into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.58,0:54:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.02,0:54:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.14,0:54:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for being my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.46,0:54:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the privilege
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.00,0:54:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of being your teacher, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.00,0:55:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we have about
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.92,0:55:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,five minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.00,0:55:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,before we have to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.36,0:55:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.70,0:55:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.40,0:55:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was said
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.30,0:55:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's individual karma
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.30,0:55:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.24,0:55:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And also,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.74,0:55:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no personal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.56,0:55:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And is there any way
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.52,0:55:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.22,0:55:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the seeming difference
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.12,0:55:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,between those?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.18,0:55:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.76,0:55:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat it one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.08,0:55:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because the microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.90,0:55:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,was...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.20,0:55:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,First, make one sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.54,0:55:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was said
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.04,0:55:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there was individual karma
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.28,0:55:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.82,0:55:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have individual karma
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.08,0:55:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.34,0:55:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.26,0:55:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there was individual karma
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.88,0:55:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.00,0:55:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.86,0:55:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's also been said
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.15,0:55:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no personal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.88,0:55:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no personal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.44,0:55:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no personal you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.71,0:55:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or personal...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.42,0:55:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're mixing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.13,0:55:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.61,0:55:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.36,0:55:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mixing levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.46,0:55:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.92,0:55:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's true at this level
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.03,0:55:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is not explicable
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.42,0:55:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same language
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.00,0:55:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.34,0:56:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was the second part
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.59,0:56:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of your question you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.26,0:56:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just to...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.53,0:56:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was explainable
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.71,0:56:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,why they seem to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.63,0:56:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't seem to be able
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.90,0:56:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.46,0:56:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what the question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.31,0:56:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.53,0:56:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.92,0:56:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to know
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.75,0:56:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.48,0:56:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's my confusion about it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.65,0:56:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.85,0:56:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because if there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.11,0:56:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like personal
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.09,0:56:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and individual
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.81,0:56:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.73,0:56:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.46,0:56:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And individual
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.31,0:56:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.83,0:56:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have individual karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.00,0:56:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm choosing...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.77,0:56:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If I choose and do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.61,0:56:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.63,0:56:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the karma of that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.37,0:56:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.46,0:56:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's going to make
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.17,0:56:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,my level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.23,0:56:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,go up or down
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.11,0:56:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,based on my intention
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.31,0:56:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.42,0:56:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.53,0:56:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,personal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.50,0:56:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it may have no effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.98,0:56:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.31,0:56:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it may not have no effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.46,0:56:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but that would be personal
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.40,0:56:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to me, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.65,0:56:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.21,0:56:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.05,0:57:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.53,0:57:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite self
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.57,0:57:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is uninfluenced
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.69,0:57:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,by what the small self
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.03,0:57:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.92,0:57:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.61,0:57:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.53,0:57:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite self,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.55,0:57:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite self,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.61,0:57:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't even register
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.27,0:57:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what the small self
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.33,0:57:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.03,0:57:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the sun shines
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.59,0:57:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,on all equally,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.98,0:57:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.55,0:57:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's mayhem
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.88,0:57:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,or a peace march,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.29,0:57:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all the same
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.15,0:57:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.19,0:57:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.33,0:57:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.00,0:57:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.61,0:57:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.50,0:57:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.42,0:57:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.48,0:57:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So this...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.40,0:57:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The small self
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.57,0:57:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.96,0:57:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.26,0:57:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the large self...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.61,0:57:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.13,0:57:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the large S...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.00,0:57:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, is the self...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.24,0:57:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.88,0:57:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.46,0:57:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.59,0:57:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.90,0:57:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.44,0:57:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.92,0:57:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that part is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.46,0:57:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.80,0:57:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.90,0:57:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.53,0:57:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.26,0:58:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And the self with the small S
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.01,0:58:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is your ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.86,0:58:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.42,0:58:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.61,0:58:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That comes and goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.00,0:58:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.38,0:58:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that explain it a little better?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.51,0:58:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.78,0:58:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.53,0:58:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.40,0:58:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.07,0:58:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.90,0:58:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.92,0:58:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.76,0:58:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.88,0:58:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,about a 10-minute break
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.05,0:58:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.44,0:58:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remember
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.38,0:58:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,your place in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.92,0:58:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.59,0:58:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
